<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Activate Your Account</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+3:wght@200..900&display=swap" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .logo-box {
            background-color: #d4eff8;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        }
        .logo-box img {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 160px;
            height: auto;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2d2d2d;
        }
        .activation-code {
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            color: #ba3d4f;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #888;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #888;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer p {
            font-size: 10px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer .unsubscribe-link {
            color: #ba3d4f;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer .unsubscribe-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="logo-box">
            <img src={{logoUrl}} alt="Logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Activate Your Account</h1>
            <p><strong>Hi {{name}},</strong></p>
            <p>
                Thank you for signing up with DataAnno! To activate your account,
                please use the following 6-digit activation code:
            </p>
            <div class="activation-code">{{activationCode}}</div>
            <p>
                Enter this code in the activation form to complete the process. If you did not sign up for this account,
                you can safely ignore this email.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Copyright 2024 DataAnno. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href={{privacyPolicy}}>Privacy Policy</a> | <a href={{termsOfService}}>Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                If you no longer wish to receive these emails, you can <a href={{unsubscribeLink}} class="unsubscribe-link">unsubscribe
                    here</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>